graph TD
    A[交互场景分析] --> B{场景类型?}
    B -->|高频动画| C[仅 transform/opacity]
    B -->|内容变更| D[content-visibility: auto]
    B -->|复杂列表| E[虚拟化 + requestIdleCallback]
    B -->|用户输入| F[防抖/节流 + CSS过渡]
    B -->|性能达标检查| G[Web Vitals 行业基准]
    
    C --> C1[Compositor Thread 独立处理]
    C --> C2[避开 Layout + Paint]
    C --> C3[GPU 直接处理]
    
    D --> D1[延迟视口外渲染]
    D --> D2[contain-intrinsic-size]
    
    E --> E1[只渲染视口内节点]
    E --> E2[复用 DOM 节点]
    E --> E3[空闲时间预渲染]
    
    F --> F1[控制 JS 执行频率]
    F --> F2[CSS 处理视觉反馈]
    F --> F3[避免主线程阻塞]
    
    G --> G1[LCP &lt; 2.5s Good]
    G --> G2[INP &lt; 200ms Good]
    G --> G3[CLS &lt; 0.1 Good]
    G --> G4[TTFB &lt; 0.8s Good]
    G --> G5[FCP &lt; 1.8s Good]
    
    style A fill:#f9f,stroke:#333
    style C fill:#bfb,stroke:#333
    style D fill:#bfb,stroke:#333
    style E fill:#bfb,stroke:#333
    style F fill:#bfb,stroke:#333
    style G fill:#bbf,stroke:#333
